(## Deployment Pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The intended path is:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(local repo -> git -> Replit -> Sipopedia.com) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For that pipeline to stay connected, every environment needs the right public frontend variables) Tj
T*
(and private backend secrets.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Required Production Environment Variables) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Set these in Replit or the deployment environment:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(VITE_APP_URL=https://sipopedia.com) Tj
T*
(VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co) Tj
T*
(VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Server-side or Edge Function secrets should remain private:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co) Tj
T*
(SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key) Tj
T*
(SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<private-service-role-key>) Tj
T*
(GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=<private-google-ai-key>) Tj
T*
(GOOGLE_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Never commit real values for private secrets.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Supabase Redirect URLs) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Supabase Auth URL configuration should allow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(https://sipopedia.com) Tj
T*
(https://www.sipopedia.com) Tj
T*
(http://localhost:3000) Tj
T*
(http://127.0.0.1:5173) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Production should use `https://sipopedia.com`. Local development can use `localhost` only when) Tj
T*
(the local dev server is running.) Tj
T*
(If testing on a temporary Replit URL, add that exact URL to Supabase Auth redirect URLs and do) Tj
T*
(not set `VITE_APP_URL` to a localhost URL.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
