(## Secret Handling Rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Safe to expose in frontend:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `VITE_APP_URL`) Tj
T*
(- `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`) Tj
T*
(- `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`) Tj
T*
(- `VITE_CHECKOUT_URL`) Tj
T*
(- `VITE_SALES_EMAIL`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Keep private:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`) Tj
T*
(- `GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY`) Tj
T*
(- OAuth client secrets) Tj
T*
(- downloaded OAuth JSON files) Tj
T*
(- billing webhook secrets) Tj
T*
(- any file containing real tokens) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Verification Completed) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The fix was validated with:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(npm run build) Tj
T*
(powershell -File .\\validators\\validate-website.ps1 -SkipInstall) Tj
T*
(npm run security:secrets) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(All passed before the fix was pushed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Git Result) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The fix was pushed to `main` in commit:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```text) Tj
T*
(1a4efd3 Harden Supabase auth callback handling) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Operational Checklist) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Before publishing:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Confirm Replit has `VITE_APP_URL=https://sipopedia.com`.) Tj
T*
(2. Confirm Replit has the current Supabase frontend variables.) Tj
T*
(3. Confirm Supabase Edge Function secrets are stored in Supabase/Replit secret stores, not git.) Tj
T*
(4. Confirm Supabase Auth redirect URLs include `https://sipopedia.com`.) Tj
T*
(5. Publish from the latest `main`.) Tj
T*
(6. Test Google login on `https://sipopedia.com`.) Tj
T*
